reviews.text: Awesome tasty food with good quantity and quality would recommend to everyone...owner was so polite and helpful and food was tasty

Great Indian food, like back in the UK. Cooked to order. Not cheap but worth it. Place is small but staff are friendly.

Edit - went for takeaway today. Your standard rogan josh and chicken tikka Masala, but both were hotter than usual, hotter than vindaloo. Called to let them know, but suddenly they couldn't understand English anymore. Shame.

Small little Induan restaurant inside a shopping mall. The quality of the the food is very good, nice and spicy. There are no views here, the service is good and polite. Usually able to get a table without much effort. The prices are moderate.

Super good little Indian place upstairs in the kfc mall in Fo Tan. I am however, just a random guilo so mind you Im far from an indian food specialist. The nan was so fresh and soft. 5 stars for the nan...bread..stuff for sure. Curry chicken was super good. Good amount of cumin in there which worked very well with the chicken and nan. 65 hkd for the plate in the pic which is definitely reasonable. Ill go back next week no questions asked. Awesome job they do here✌️✌️✌️

Amazing restaurant! One of my favorite uwu :3
It's actually really good tbh (♡∀♡）
I really love the mango drink... the mango lassi :) it's so goodddddddd~

reviews.text: Used to be good 2 - 3 years ago as they do have nice servers. Now, you gotta order fast, eat fast, pay asap, and leave asap. No No No.

relaxing cafe. 

provide free parking, if  bills over hkd$200
Nice place
話坐底飲, 竟然都俾隻外買杯收多我倆蚊,, 太cheap lah,, 另外, 食物一般中的一般, coffee我個人覺得太甜

完成工作，與朋友就到附近既餐廳搵食，嘆一下下午茶。雖然係下午茶時間，但我地三人均未食午餐，所以我地點餐都係同午餐無分別。我自己就點左個鰻魚蛋飯食，$77連野飲，價錢唔平，但黎到其實賣相不錯。食落口也算中上，味道ok，蛋夠滑鰻魚夠香，不過鰻魚就有點難咬口。至於朋友就食意粉，味道也是不錯的，整體上ok。另外我地還有點一客蒜蓉包，只有四塊再加杯野飲要$36，還可以吧！如果價錢可以相宜一點，這間應該會很受歡迎，不過依家百物騰貴，也是可以理解的。
